l did not know the things that we know now, and that&rsquo;s totally OK; we all start somewhere. Learning new material is an exciting adventure, especially if you are looking to learn the subject efficiently.<br />\n<br />\n最近讀過既野，同你分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469c7cf12f80a711fb1fda665b444fab25a654fd","tid":591262,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82cf001477baf117fc4be757845c546e3b2292fe","tid":591262,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"354f4fe94bbd8bc5176f803d8b47bfd5192e7cfe","tid":591262,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"我都要人陪 <br />\n我陪你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"你唔開心？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"係。<br />\n同朋友疏遠左好多 感覺返唔到去以前咁<br />\n另外，追緊個女仔 佢對我忽冷忽熱 睇唔透佢諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc89c3e5b6e57f9c8ea7897b29a8d79580317586","tid":591262,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27187d7f164228b48cba0ca2efca6512300488a3","tid":591262,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d94ed9878cf3610381d5e11e36c38620b12e147","tid":591262,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:06:51.000Z","msg":"橫豎你也是得一個人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"讀我一間u 一個課<br />\n來為我未來一一探問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"38229ccefb568c73501abceb5403b795ef95691e","tid":591262,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57091825d4b376024521768a7d34b37e8705d48e","tid":591262,"uid":173050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216aeddf6c5ade551c3a6ab57bce2b3554855f83","tid":591262,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241588316cdc8500c2934b404cb895ed1517c1b7","tid":591262,"ui